---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="DevPlaybook terms of service — usage rules, intellectual property, and disclaimers."
  noindex={false}
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-invert">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 15, 2026</p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        By accessing and using DevPlaybook (<a href="https://devplaybook.cc" class="text-primary hover:underline">devplaybook.cc</a>), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use the site.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        DevPlaybook provides free browser-based developer tools, curated software resources, technical blog articles, and optional premium products. All tools run entirely in your browser — no data is transmitted to our servers.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">3. Free Tools</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        Our developer tools (JSON formatter, regex tester, UUID generator, etc.) are provided free of charge for personal and commercial use. You may use outputs generated by these tools without restriction. We make no guarantee of uptime or availability.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">4. Premium Products</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        Premium products (Pro subscription, bundles, individual products) are sold through Gumroad. Purchases are subject to Gumroad's terms of service and refund policy. Digital products are delivered immediately upon purchase.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">
        All content on DevPlaybook — including articles, tool code, design, and graphics — is owned by DevPlaybook unless otherwise stated. You may:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-text-muted space-y-1">
        <li>Share links to any page</li>
        <li>Quote short excerpts with attribution</li>
        <li>Use code snippets from blog posts in your own projects</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
        You may not reproduce, redistribute, or resell entire articles or products without permission.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">6. User Conduct</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">You agree not to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-text-muted space-y-1 mt-2">
        <li>Attempt to disrupt or overload the site</li>
        <li>Scrape content in bulk for automated redistribution</li>
        <li>Use the site for any unlawful purpose</li>
        <li>Misrepresent DevPlaybook content as your own original work</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        DevPlaybook is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind, express or implied. We do not guarantee that the site will be error-free, uninterrupted, or that any information is accurate or up-to-date. Developer tools are provided for convenience and should not be relied upon as the sole source of truth for production systems.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        To the maximum extent permitted by law, DevPlaybook shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of the site, tools, or products.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">9. Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        DevPlaybook contains links to third-party websites and tools. We are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or availability of external sites. Links do not imply endorsement.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">10. Advertising</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        DevPlaybook may display advertisements through Google AdSense and other advertising networks. Ad content is provided by third parties and does not represent our views or endorsement.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">11. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">12. Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        For questions about these terms, please visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
